---
title: Grilled Honey-Glazed Sausage Patties with Stone Fruit and Wild Rice Medley
description: Grilled sausage patties–kissed with smoky honey, torn fresh basil and nectarines–is what warm weather is all about! It'll become a new favourite flavour combination.

